[src:floyd-warshall-algorithm/weighted-graph-p02] An oriented graph is one that has been assigned an orientation.
[src:floyd-warshall-algorithm/weighted-graph-p02] is an oriented tree; it differs from a directed tree (an arborescence) in that there is no requirement of consistency in the directions of its edges.
